{"tid":339869,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"放心！《復仇者3》會解釋清楚每粒無限寶石做乜","createTime":"2017-07-29T12:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:07:38.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"298d768da29902bc686d00b093d1159ca2c33d5b","tid":339869,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=25406&amp;catid=35\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D25406%26catid%3D35&h=5c9be284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》奸角Thanos使用無限手套，六粒無限寶石各具異能，控制空間、靈魂、現實、時間、力量同心靈，導演羅索兄弟Joe Russo稱電影會搵到方式去畀觀眾分辨到每粒寶石嘅能力，包括較難表達同解釋嘅現實寶石。<br />\n現實寶石能夠隨使用者想法去改變現實，甚至可以違反現實及邏輯，目前5粒無限寶石分別喺之前多部Marvel作品內登場，而剩低嘅靈魂寶石應該會喺《雷神奇俠3：神域末日》出現。Joe稱團隊花好多心思去具體表達各寶石異能，加上電影出場角色亦係好多，因此難度都幾高。<br />\n資料來源:Screenrant"},{"pid":"1bb58c45fe1344c0c9af27fff6211ba14d4715b8","tid":339869,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:07:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=25406&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D25406%26catid%3D35&d=BJqaAaJictGLrTxXk8k3beargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=06744f97\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=25406&amp;catid=35</a>"}]}